@template block_event_management/topicsmain
@description This template displays forum topic statistics for courses.
It expects the following context data:
- access: Boolean indicating if the user has permission to access this page.
- topicsdata: Array containing statistics for topics within forums, each element includes:
  - course: The name of the course.
  - forums: The name of the forum.
  - topics: The title of the topic.
  - posts: The total number of posts in the topic.
  - postanswers: The number of replies to posts within the topic.
  - initialized: Indicates whether the topic was initialized by the user.
  - postreads: The number of times posts were read within the topic.
  - courseid: The ID of the course.
  - forumid: The ID of the forum.
  - topicid: The ID of the topic.
  - viewusers: URL for viewing user details related to the topic.
  - from: The start date for the search period.
  - to: The end date for the search period.
  - searchperiod: The specific period being filtered for the data.
- bcmbcourses: URL for the breadcrumb link back to the courses overview.
- bcmbforums: URL for the breadcrumb link back to the forums overview.
- paramcourseid: Parameter used for linking back to specific course details.
- current_lang: The current language code used for localization.
- js: Boolean indicating if JavaScript should be included for DataTable functionality.
}}

{{#access}}
    <div class="page-wrapper">

        <!-- PAGE CONTENT-->
        <div class="page-content--bgf7">

            <!-- STATISTIC MENU-->
            {{> block_course_statistics/admin/common/navsection }}
            <!-- END STATISTIC MENU -->

            <!-- Filter Table Form -->
            {{> block_course_statistics/admin/common/formsection }}
            <!-- END Filter Table Form -->

            <!-- DATA TABLE-->
